<p>Select a video and press upload. You will be given a link you can share with others.</p>
<p>Links automatically expire. Once a link expires, the video is deleted.</p>

<form action="/upload" method="POST" enctype="multipart/form-data">
  <input type="file" name="video" required />
  <label for="link-expiration">Link expiration</label>
  <select id="link-expiration" name="expirationMinutes">
    <option value="10">10 Minutes</option>
    <option value="30">30 Minutes</option>
  </select>
  <button>Upload</button>
</form>

